(123, 1, '2018-09-07 17:12:33', '2018-09-07 14:12:33', 'Paris, this city causes a lot of associations for every person, whether he was there or just wants to visit. The Eiffel tower, the Champs Elysees, croissants, Haute Couture, tennis and football tournaments, beauty and avant – garde, tradition and innovation-all combine one of the largest and most visited cities in the world.\r\n\r\nTo visit Paris, you do not need special occasions or anniversaries – the capital of France is ready for everyone to discover its most attractive features – lovers and businessmen, families with children and single travelers living in luxury hotels and visitors to numerous hostels. At any time of the year you need to go to Paris to recharge your batteries and inspiration for new achievements and creativity.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Trip to France', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trip-to-france', '', '', '2018-09-17 01:06:50', '2018-09-16 22:06:50', '', 0, 'http://mynomadtales.com/?p=123', 0, 'post', '', 0),
